m\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33708,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/10\/13\/former-enemies-embrace-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":21680,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Da&#8217;wah: Former enemies, prisoners embrace Islam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 13, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah marvels at people who enter Paradise in chains.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3010 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari Ibn al-Jawzi said, \u201cIt means they are taken prisoner and detained, but when they recognize the rightness of Islam,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27899,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/20\/cannot-claim-specific-person-is-martyr\/","url_meta":{"origin":21680,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Martyrdom: Cannot claim a specific person is a martyr","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 20, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu al-\u2018Ajfa reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cYou say about those who are killed or died in your campaigns that \u2018this person was killed as a martyr\u2019 or \u2018this person died as a martyr.\u2019 Perhaps he only intended to load his animal with spoils,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"a